<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226846>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2 – 7. Cylindroiulus julesverni n. sp. male gonopod. 2 – 3: mesal view, 4: pro- & mesomerite, anterior view, 5 – 6: lateral view, 7: opisthomerite, posterior view. afl: anterior flagellum-conducting lamella, f: flagellum, fl: flagelliferous lobe of promerite, fp: finger-shaped projection of promerite, m: mesomerite, p: promerite, pc: lateral rim of paracoxite, pfl: posterior flagellum-conducting lamella, pp: paracoxal process, s: solenomerite, sc: sperm channel. Scale bar: 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226846/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

